{
 "name": "RPlog_On_Dathomir",
 "title": "On Dathomir",
 "summary": "Stranded on the wild world of Dathomir after a crash, a small unit of New Republic personnel under orders from Inrokana makes camp in makeshift camouflage, swapping flight gear for the bush. Around a crackling fire, the pilot Raxis Dante and the markswoman Leyanne trade wary, half-joking talk about whether their uneasy situation will end peacefully or with blasters, while Leyanne field-strips and cleans her rifle. The dark-skinned crewmember blends into the night as the group settles into the tense quiet of survival on the witch-world.",
